name: Clempt Dark Red
name_cn: 克兰朋工装裤 暗红色
description:
Stegman's factory pants have been taken to the next level with the Clempt line. These rugged all-purpose pants come with double knees for extra comfort and protection and are made from tough composite weave fabric to last as long as the work needs.
Women's sizes currently out of stock.
description_cn:
施特格曼的工厂裤子已在克兰朋工装裤系列中被提升到了一个全新的高度.这款坚固耐用的多用途裤子配有双护膝,可提供额外的舒适度和防护,并且由坚固的复合编织面料制成,工作多久穿多久.
女款目前缺货.
